name: tylermolamphy/dots
body:
This is where I house all of my .dotfiles that host configuation for vim, zsh, aliases, and many other things I feel that I'd rather not live without on a Unix comand line.

***
git clone git@github.com:tylermolamphy/dots.git
cd !$
./bootstrap
***

Feel free to fork the repo and tinker with it, share it, what's mine is yours.
It's up for my own use, but you're welcome to make it your own :)

tyler@tylermolamphy.com with any questions
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
